---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import VideoTrimmer from '../components/VideoTrimmer.tsx';
---

<Layout
	title="Video Trimmer - Cut & Trim Videos Online Free | QuickEditVideo"
	description="Trim videos online with precision! Cut unwanted parts from MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV files. No uploads, no sign-up. Free video trimmer that works in your browser."
	keywords="video trimmer, trim video online, cut video, video cutter, free video trimmer, MP4 trimmer, WebM trimmer, AVI trimmer, MOV trimmer, online video editor"
	ogTitle="Free Online Video Trimmer - Cut Videos with Precision"
	ogDescription="Professional video trimming tool. Cut videos with frame-perfect precision. Works with all major formats. No uploads required - completely private and secure."
	canonicalUrl="https://quickeditvideo.com/trim"
>
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
		<!-- Page Header -->
		<div id="page-header" class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 py-6 transition-all duration-300">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Video Trimmer</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Cut videos with frame-perfect precision</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Video Editor -->
		<section class="p-4 md:p-6 w-full">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
				<VideoTrimmer client:load />
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Quick Help -->
		<section id="quick-help" class="px-4 md:px-6 pb-16">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Quick Guide</h3>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					<!-- Step 1: Upload -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all p-6 text-center">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
							<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-teal-600">
								<path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/>
								<polyline points="14,2 14,8 20,8"/>
								<path d="M10 15.5L16 12L10 8.5V15.5Z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 mx-auto">1</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Upload Video</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Upload your video file (supports MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV)</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Step 2: Trim -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all p-6 text-center">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
							<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-teal-600">
								<path d="M20 4L3 11l3 3l4-2l2 4Z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 mx-auto">2</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Set Timeline</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Drag timeline handles to set start and end points</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Step 3: Download -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all p-6 text-center">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
							<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-teal-600">
								<path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
								<polyline points="7,10 12,15 17,10"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 mx-auto">3</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Download Result</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Preview your selection and download the trimmed video</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Content Section for SEO -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 md:px-6">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Introduction -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Video Trimmer That Actually Gets It</h2>
					<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-4">
						<p>
							Let's be honest—you shouldn't need a film degree just to cut a few seconds off your video. Whether you're trimming a presentation recording, cutting highlights from a longer clip, or removing awkward pauses from your content, video editing software often feels like overkill.
						</p>
						<p>
							That's exactly why we built this tool. No downloads, no accounts, no monthly subscriptions. Just drag your video file, set your start and end points, and download your perfectly trimmed clip. Your video never leaves your device, so your privacy stays intact.
						</p>
						<p>
							If you can drag a slider, you can master this tool in under 30 seconds. Because your time matters more than learning another complicated interface.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- How It Works -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">How Our Video Trimmer Works</h3>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Upload & Process Locally</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								Drop your video file directly into the browser. Everything happens on your device using WebAssembly technology—no servers involved, no waiting for uploads.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Precise Timeline Control</h4>
