							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Will trimming reduce my video quality?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">No quality loss at all. We use frame-perfect cutting without re-encoding, so your trimmed video maintains the exact same quality as your original.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I use this on my phone or tablet?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes! The tool works on any device with a modern web browser, including smartphones and tablets. The interface adapts to your screen size.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What happens to my original video file?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Your original file remains completely untouched. The tool creates a new trimmed copy for download, so you always keep your source material.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What video formats are supported?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">We support all major video formats including MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV, MKV, and more. If your browser can play it, we can trim it.</p>
						</div>
						
